# pipenv-uv

[![PyPI - Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/pipenv-uv.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/pipenv-uv)
[![PyPI - Python Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/pipenv-uv.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/pipenv-uv)
